@startuml
title Viaverse Job Lifecycle — State Diagram

[*] --> CREATED : quote accepted
CREATED --> WAITING_PAYMENT
WAITING_PAYMENT --> READY_TO_START : PaymentAuthorized
READY_TO_START --> IN_PROGRESS : worker starts
IN_PROGRESS --> DELIVERED : deliver
DELIVERED --> REVISION_REQUESTED : needs fix
REVISION_REQUESTED --> IN_PROGRESS : redeliver work
DELIVERED --> COMPLETED : approved
COMPLETED --> PAYOUT_ELIGIBLE : payout eligible
READY_TO_START --> CANCELLED : cancel allowed
IN_PROGRESS --> DISPUTED : problem
DELIVERED --> DISPUTED : dispute
DISPUTED --> REFUNDED : resolved refund
DISPUTED --> COMPLETED : resolved complete

PAYOUT_ELIGIBLE --> [*]
CANCELLED --> [*]
REFUNDED --> [*]

note bottom
COMPLETED proceeds to review/payout.
CANCELLED/REFUNDED close the job.
DISPUTED blocks payout until resolved.
end note
@enduml
